    "description": {
      "description": "<p>Solução ácida feita com reagentes químicos.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Uso:</span> Líquido, ou Arremesso.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Alcance:</span> 7/21m.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Dano:</span> 13+COG/2 Elemental: Cáustico.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Efeitos:</span> prévio ao dano, causa [2+<span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family:'MS Mincho';mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">Ⓐ</span>] de dano Destrutivo. Se aplicado sobre uma pequena superfície, causa [2] de dano Destrutivo por minuto no decorrer de 10 minutos.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Preço:</span> 50 cobres.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Ofício:</span> Alquimia N2.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Tempo para fabricar:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> 1 hora.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Materiais:</span> 1<span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:8.0pt;line-height:105%;mso-fareast-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\"> Reagente.</span></p>",
